2017年'''伊德利卜省衝突'''是[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]反政府武裝組織之間的武裝衝突，主要在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]及[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]西部發生。

==事前態勢==
敘利亞[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]的反政府武裝可以粗略分為兩大派，一派以[[自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動|自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動]]為首，另一派則以原為[[基地组织|基地组织]]分支的[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]為首。2016年10月，自由沙姆人伊斯蘭運動與源自征服沙姆陣線的[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]在伊德利卜省爆發[[2016年伊德利卜省衝突|激烈衝突]]，導致後者的大部分成員向征服沙姆陣線宣稱效忠。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=52997|title=Tension return between Jund al-Aqsa and Ahrar al-Sham in the countryside of Idlib and shooting in al-Suwaidaa|work=Syria HR|date=2016-10-22|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220214546/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=52997|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年1月美軍空襲造成[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]有超過100人被炸死後，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.defense.gov/News/Article/Article/1055727/us-airstrike-kills-more-than-100-al-qaida-fighters-in-syria|title=U.S. Airstrike Kills More Than 100 al-Qaida Fighters in Syria|work=US Department of Defense|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814234613/https://www.defense.gov/News/Article/Article/1055727/us-airstrike-kills-more-than-100-al-qaida-fighters-in-syria/|dead-url=no}}</ref>征服沙姆陣線指控有敵對武裝組織向美軍提供目標信息。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalresearch.ca/syrian-war-report-isis-repelled-heavy-clashes-between-ahrar-al-sham-and-al-nusra-in-idlib/5569996 |title=Syrian War Report: ISIS Repelled, Heavy Clashes between Ahrar Al-Sham and Al-Nusra in Idlib |accessdate=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921010615/https://www.globalresearch.ca/syrian-war-report-isis-repelled-heavy-clashes-between-ahrar-al-sham-and-al-nusra-in-idlib/5569996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==2017年1月==
2017年1月20日，[[征服沙姆陣線|征服沙姆陣線]]向自由沙姆人在[[伊德利卜省|伊德利卜省]]北部的總部和據點發動攻擊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/@_alhamra/why-al-qaeda-jfs-is-attacking-ahrar-al-sham-by-charles-lister-4b49affca03|title=Why Al-Qaeda/JFS Is Attacking Ahrar al-Sham: @charles_lister’s Take|work=Medium Corporation|author=Al-Hamra|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022052809/https://medium.com/@_alhamra/why-al-qaeda-jfs-is-attacking-ahrar-al-sham-by-charles-lister-4b49affca03|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]突襲自由沙姆人在Jabal Zawiya的一所監獄，救出被囚的13名己方成員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/trouble-jihadist-paradise-rival-factions-battle-idlib/|title=Trouble in jihadist paradise as rival factions battle in Idlib|work=Al-Masdar News|author=Leith Fadel|date=2017-01-20|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203132405/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/trouble-jihadist-paradise-rival-factions-battle-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>征服沙姆陣線也在同一地區攻擊[[自由伊德利卜軍|自由伊德利卜軍]]的[[山鷹旅|山鷹旅]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alnour.com.lb/ar/news/security/2017-01-21_061848/%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%81-%D8%A5%D8%AF%D9%84%D8%A8-%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%B5%D9%82%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D8%A8%D9%84-%D9%88%D8%AC%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B5%D8%B1%D8%A9|title=Clashes in the countryside of Idlib between the "Brigade Hawks Mountain" and "Front victory"|work=Nour Radio|date=2017-01-21|access-date=2017-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202013304/http://www.alnour.com.lb/ar/news/security/2017-01-21_061848/%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%81-%D8%A5%D8%AF%D9%84%D8%A8-%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%B5%D9%82%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AC%D8%A8%D9%84-%D9%88%D8%AC%D8%A8%D9%87%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B5%D8%B1%D8%A9|archive-date=2017-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

1月23日，征服沙姆陣線宣佈從其隊伍中驅逐[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]，不過衝突仍然持續。<ref name=mee1>{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/rebel-fighting-idlib-increases-tensions-over-peace-talks-2113068507|title=Syrian rebels threaten to 'annihilate' rivals as Idlib infighting rages|work=Middle East Eye|author=Alex MacDonald|date=2017-01-23|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124132455/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/rebel-fighting-idlib-increases-tensions-over-peace-talks-2113068507|dead-url=no}}</ref>征服沙姆陣線在[[努爾丁·贊吉運動|努爾丁·贊吉運動]]協助下攻佔[[聖戰者軍|聖戰者軍]]在[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]西部的總部。他們也攻擊在Haritan的[[沙姆陣線|沙姆陣線]]。<ref name=moj/>

到1月24日，戰敗的聖戰者軍加入自由沙姆人。<ref name=join>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/48837/Jayesh_Al_Mujahdeen_Join_Ahrar_Al_Sham_Movement|title=Mujahideen Army announces joining Freedom Movement Sham|work=Qasioun News Agency|date=2017-01-24|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019055413/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/48837/Jayesh_Al_Mujahdeen_Join_Ahrar_Al_Sham_Movement|dead-url=no}}</ref>自由沙姆人派出一些部隊到伊德利卜省郊區和[[阿勒頗省|阿勒頗省]]西部抵禦征服沙姆陣線的進攻。征服沙姆陣線對伊德利卜省郊區一處聖戰者軍總部的進攻被[[沙姆軍團|沙姆軍團]]擊退。<ref name=fail>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/48782/Fateh_Al_Sham_Fail_To_Raid_Jayesh_Al_Mujahdeen_Centres|title=Fateh Al-Sham Fail To Raid Jayesh Al-Mujahdeen Centres|work=Qasioun News Agency|date=2017-01-24|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202020452/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/48782/Fateh_Al_Sham_Fail_To_Raid_Jayesh_Al_Mujahdeen_Centres|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1月25日，征服沙姆陣線從[[沙姆之隼旅|沙姆之隼旅]]手上攻佔伊德利卜中央監獄。<ref name=crush>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-group-idUSKBN1591AF |title=Jihadists crush Syria rebel group, in a blow to diplomacy |work=Reuters |author=Tom Perry |date=2017-01-25 |accessdate=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2019-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510055147/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-group-idUSKBN1591AF |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1月26日，自由沙姆人與盟友從征服沙姆陣線手上攻佔Jabal Zawiya地區北部的一些村莊。<ref name="Idlib clashes map">{{cite web|url=http://imgur.com/a/h5C3P|title=Idlib governorate clashes|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-05|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019055709/https://imgur.com/a/h5C3P|dead-url=no}}</ref>忠於征服沙姆陣線的武裝分子從敵對反對派手上攻佔Halfaya鎮。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobile.almasdarnews.com/article/situation-northern-hama-becomes-worrisome-jihadists-take/|title=Situation in northern Hama becomes worrisome as jihadists take over|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2017-01-26|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019060012/https://mobile.almasdarnews.com/article/situation-northern-hama-becomes-worrisome-jihadists-take/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>次日，征服沙姆陣線攻擊[[伊斯蘭軍|伊斯蘭軍]]在伊德利卜省北部的總部。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.all4syria.info/Archive/383174|title=(Fatah al-Sham) are attacking the headquarters of the (Army of Islam) in the northern Idlib Babsaga|work=All4Syria|date=2017-01-27|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127175055/http://www.all4syria.info/Archive/383174|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1月28日，征服沙姆陣線與其它數個聖戰分子團體組成「[[沙姆解放組織|沙姆解放組織]]」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mobile.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN15C0MV|title=Syria Islamist factions, including former al Qaeda branch, join forces: statement|date=2017-01-28|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129060723/http://mobile.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN15C0MV|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==2017年2月==
2017年2月7日，[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]攻擊勝利軍在[[哈馬省|哈馬省]]北部Murak鎮附近的總部。阿克薩戰士攻佔[[卡夫爾齊塔|卡夫爾齊塔]]（Kafr Zita）鎮，並突襲Taybat al-Imam鎮，<ref name=zone>{{cite web|url=http://www.alhadathnews.net/archives/272995|title="Jund al-Aqsa" seize the headquarters of the "free" and declared a military zone in Hama and Idlib|work=Al-Hadath News|date=2017-02-08|access-date=2017-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009213524/http://www.alhadathnews.net/archives/272995|archive-date=2017-10-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>俘虜了超過250名勝利軍成員並擄獲一些武器。<ref name=250p>{{cite web|url=http://aletihadpress.com/2017/02/07/%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%82%D8%B5%D9%89-%D9%8A%D9%87%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%82%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AC%D9%8A%D8%B4-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%81/|title=Al-Aqsa Brigade attacked the headquarters of an army victory Brive northern Hama|work=Al-Etihad Press|date=2017-02-07|access-date=2017-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080459/http://aletihadpress.com/2017/02/07/%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%82%D8%B5%D9%89-%D9%8A%D9%87%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%82%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%AC%D9%8A%D8%B4-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%81/|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2月9日，阿克薩戰士攻佔Ajnad al-Sham和其它一些反對派武裝在卡夫爾齊塔一帶及哈馬省北部郊區其它地方的總部，又擄獲不少武器和裝備。阿克薩戰士到這時候在哈馬省北部和伊德利卜省南部已控制17個城鎮和村莊。<ref name="controls">{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=60582|title=Jund al-Aqsa organization controls 17 villages, towns and cities in the countryside of Idlib and Hama|publisher=SOHR|author=|date=2017-02-09|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211083009/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=60582|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="overrun">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/salafist-jihadists-overrun-fsa-northern-syria-rebel-infighting-intensifies/|title=Salafist jihadists overrun FSA in northern Syria as rebel infighting intensifies|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=2017-02-09|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-11|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224172004/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/salafist-jihadists-overrun-fsa-northern-syria-rebel-infighting-intensifies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月13日，原為盟友的[[沙姆解放組織|沙姆解放組織]]與[[阿克薩戰士|阿克薩戰士]]在哈馬省北部及伊德利卜省南部爆發衝突。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2017/02/13/jihadist-rebel-groups-clash-in-northwest-syria--monitor/|title=Jihadist rebel groups clash in northwest Syria – monitor|work=Reuters|date=2017-02-13|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213120204/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2017/02/13/jihadist-rebel-groups-clash-in-northwest-syria--monitor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙姆解放組織向阿克薩戰士宣戰，雙方共有約70人在衝突中喪生。<ref name=ap>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-state-media-says-talks-should-focus-on-terrorism/2017/02/14/079879a8-f29f-11e6-9fb1-2d8f3fc9c0ed_story.html?utm_term=.f57a7db4955d|title=Clashes between 2 extremist groups kill scores in Syria|work=Associated Press|author=Bassem Mroue|date=2017-02-14|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217223746/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/syrian-state-media-says-talks-should-focus-on-terrorism/2017/02/14/079879a8-f29f-11e6-9fb1-2d8f3fc9c0ed_story.html?utm_term=.f57a7db4955d|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月14日，阿克薩戰士宣佈已處決超過100名戰俘，<ref name=slaughter>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-al-qaeda-group-slaughters-100-jihadist-rebels-idlib/|title=Syrian Al-Qaeda group slaughters over 100 jihadist rebels in Idlib|author=Leith Fadel|work=al-Masdar News|date=2017-02-14|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215000327/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-al-qaeda-group-slaughters-100-jihadist-rebels-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>據報有超過160名[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]成員和43名沙姆解放組織成員被處決。<ref name=scores>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-islamists-idUSKBN15V0UM |title=Syrian jihadists kill scores of rival insurgents: rebel official, SITE |date=2017-02-16 |publisher= |via=Reuters |accessdate=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2018-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127190136/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-islamists-idUSKBN15V0UM |dead-url=no }}</ref>次日，沙姆解放組織從阿克薩戰士手上攻佔Heish村，並包圍在Khan Shaykhun鎮和Murak鎮的阿克薩戰士部隊。<ref name="Jund al-Aqsa besieged">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jund-al-aqsa-completely-besieged-rival-rebel-factions-around-two-towns-idlib/|title=Jund al-Aqsa completely besieged by rival rebel factions around two towns in Idlib|author=Chris Tomson|work=al-Masdar News|date=2017-02-16|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216220414/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jund-al-aqsa-completely-besieged-rival-rebel-factions-around-two-towns-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月19日，據報600名阿克薩戰士成員將會轉移到[[拉卡省|拉卡省]]和加入伊斯蘭國，其餘成員則將會在72小時內交出重型武器和加入[[突厥斯坦伊斯兰党|突厥斯坦伊斯兰党]]。據報至此時為止超過250名自由敘利亞軍和沙姆解放組織成員在與阿克薩戰士的衝突中喪生。<ref name="250+ killed">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/250-fighters-killed-rebel-infighting-across-syria/|title=250+ fighters killed in rebel infighting across Syria|first=Suliman|last=Mulhem|date=2017-02-19|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220171316/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/250-fighters-killed-rebel-infighting-across-syria/|dead-url=no}}</ref>當天下午，一支載有阿克薩戰士成員和親屬的車隊試圖穿過敘利亞政府控制區到拉卡省，遭到[[國防軍_(敘利亞)|國防軍]]伏擊，被迫投降。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-ambushes-scores-of-islamist-rebels-trying-to-defect-to-isis/|title=Syrian Army ambushes scores of Islamist rebels trying to defect to ISIS|last=Tomson|first=Chris|date=2017-02-19|website=Al-Masdar News|accessdate=2017-02-19|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220093112/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-ambushes-scores-of-islamist-rebels-trying-to-defect-to-isis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日沙姆解放組織突襲伊斯蘭軍在風之門邊境通道附近的據點，擄獲一些重型武器。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebel-infighting-continues-new-coalition-raids-jaysh-al-islams-positions-idlib/|title=Rebel infighting continues as new coalition raids Jaysh Al-Islam’s positions in Idlib|work=Al-Masdar News|author=Leith Fadel|date=19 February 2017|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220172537/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebel-infighting-continues-new-coalition-raids-jaysh-al-islams-positions-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月22日，經過與沙姆解放組織和[[突厥斯坦伊斯兰党|突厥斯坦伊斯兰党]]達成協議後，阿克薩旅2,100名武裝分子的最後一批人離開在Khan Skaykhun的最後據點，轉往[[拉卡省|拉卡省]]加入伊斯蘭國。<ref name="defect to ISIS">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/2000-radical-rebels-defect-isis-following-intra-rebel-deal/|title=Over 2,000 radical rebels defect to ISIS following intra-rebel deal|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=2017-02-23|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603010011/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/2000-radical-rebels-defect-isis-following-intra-rebel-deal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙姆解放組織隨後宣佈阿克薩旅已經不再存在。<ref name="declare terminating">{{cite web|url=https://news.siteintelgroup.com/Jihadist-News/tahrir-al-sham-declare-terminating-liwa-al-aqsa.html|title=Tahrir al-Sham Declare Terminating Liwa al-Aqsa|first=|last=SITE|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-15|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224213119/https://news.siteintelgroup.com/Jihadist-News/tahrir-al-sham-declare-terminating-liwa-al-aqsa.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

繼早前尋獲41名武裝分子的屍體後，人們在阿克薩旅撤出Khan Seikhoun後在當地找到兩處埋葬被阿克薩旅處決的敵對武裝分子的集體墓地，合共埋葬至少131具屍體。<ref name="130 bodies found">{{cite web|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/afp/2017/02/syria-conflict-idlib-jihadists.html|title=130 bodies found in Syria mass graves|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-22|archive-date=2017-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301181408/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/afp/2017/02/syria-conflict-idlib-jihadists.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==2017年3月==
3月2日，[[沙姆軍團|沙姆軍團]]分裂成3個團體。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/faylaq-al-sham-ground-descend-into-bitter-civil-war-in-militant-held-idlib-governorate/|title=Faylaq al-Sham group descends into bitter civil war in militant-held Idlib governorate|last=Antonopoulos|first=Paul|date=2017-03-02|work=AMN - Al-Masdar News|access-date=2017-03-03|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020013132/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/faylaq-al-sham-ground-descend-into-bitter-civil-war-in-militant-held-idlib-governorate/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/idlib-province-descends-chaos-inter-jihadist-war-intensifies/|title=Idlib province descends into further chaos as inter-jihadist war intensifies|last=Antonopoulos|first=Paul|date=2017-03-02|work=AMN - Al-Masdar News|access-date=2017-03-03|language=en|archive-date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303042155/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/idlib-province-descends-chaos-inter-jihadist-war-intensifies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月3日，自由沙姆人與沙姆解放組織在Salqin鎮爆發戰鬥。<ref name="clash in rural Idlib">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-clash-one-another-rural-idlib/|title=Jihadist rebels clash with one another in rural Idlib|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=3 March 2017|publisher=|accessdate=5 March 2017|archive-date=2017-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304115452/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-clash-one-another-rural-idlib/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

